    <td valign="top"><font size="3" color="#008000"><b>Visual Auction :</b></font><p><font
    size="3"><b>admin:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This section contains the Administration pages.&nbsp; These pages can only be
        modified by Beyond Solutions, Inc.</small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>bid:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>Pages in this section process the user's bid.&nbsp; No changes need to be made to
        these pages.</small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>buyers:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This file can be changed to add more information or graphics.</small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>dbase:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This directory contains the auction database.  There are no modifiable files in this directory.&nbsp; </small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>event1:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This directory contains Futurewatch; Automatic Email notification to users with special interest
     in certain auction items when they are posted for auction.</small>
      
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>event2:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This directory contains files which run on a schedule.&nbsp; Their function is to
        complete background processes, including billing, invoicing, auto relisting, and proxy
        bidding.&nbsp; </small></li>
    </ul>
	 <p><font size="3"><b>event5:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This script refreshes the whole site such as category counts and auction stats.</small></li>
    </ul>
	 <p><font size="3"><b>event6:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>Enables site owner to consolidate Studio window pane space after removing images.</small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>feedback:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This directory contains files which are generated 'on the fly'.&nbsp; No changes
        need to be made directly to these pages.</small></li>
    </ul>
	 <p><font size="3"><b>Functions:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This area controls many of the functions offered in the admin area. Not customizable.</small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>help:</b></font><ul>
      <li><small>This area provides assistance mainly for the front end user of the site.</small></li>
	</ul>

    <p><font size="3"><b>images:</b></font><ul>
      <li><font color="#ff0000">logo.gif</font>:&nbsp;<small>This image should be replaced with your company logo. (The image name should not be changed.)</small>
      <li><font color="#ff0000">infohere_8.gif</font>:&nbsp;<small>This image should be replaced with an image providing site info or an image map. (The image name should not be changed.)</small>
      <li><font color="#ff0000">folder.gif</font>:&nbsp;<small>This image can be replaced with an icon image which will be placed next to the categories listed on your main page as well as the category pages. You can replace it with a small image related to the theme of your site. (The image name should not be changed.)</small></li>
    </ul>
    <p><font size="3"><b>includes:</b></font><ul>
      <li><font color="#ff0080">menu_bar.cfm</font>: <small>This file can be modified to personalize 
                your menu bar site-wide. It is set up to be automatically 
                placed onto all of your pages. Currently it is a text 
                link navigation file. You may replace the text with linked images to coordinate with 
                the theme of your site.</small>
      <li> <small></small><font color="#ff0080">global_vars.cfm</font>: <small>       
                  This file should be modified with your Company Name. It is 
                a file which is automatically placed in all of your generated 
                pages.</small>
      <li> <small></small><font color="#ff0080">bodytag.html</font>: <small>This file can be 
                modified to personalize the background color, link text colors, visited link colors, and 
                active link colors. This may also be modified via the Auction 
                Administrator.</small>
      <li> <small></small><font color="#ff0080">stylesheet.css</font>: <small>This file can be modified to personalize your 
                pages site-wide. If you are familiar with using stylesheets, you can modify font 
                properties, color and background properties, text properties, box properties, and classification 
                properties.<BR></small> <small>                                 <B>No other files in this directory should be modified!</B></small></li>

    </ul>
    <p><strong>listings:</strong><small>The following directories contain automatically generated files relating to auction item listings. These do not need to be modified.</small><ul>
      <li><font color="#408080"><strong>categories:</strong></font>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files relating to categories. </small>
      
      <li><font color="#408080"><strong>details:</strong></font>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files for auction details. </small>
      
      <li><font color="#408080"><strong>featured:</strong></font>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files for featured auctions. </small>
      
    </ul>
	 <p><strong>megalist:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This  directory interfaces with bid find.<a href="http://www.bidfind.com">Bid Find</a></small><ul>
	<li>&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>messaging:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files relating to messaging.  No need to modify.</small><ul>
	<li>&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>personal:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files relating to personal info.  No need to modify.</small><ul>
      <li>&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>registration:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This 
            directory contains files relating to user registration. No need to 
            modify; although you can modify the <font color="#ff0080">user_agreement.cfm </font color="#ff0080">and <font color="#ff0080">user_agreement.html</font color="#ff0080"> </font>  to add any additional terms you deem  necessary for your site.</small><ul>
      <li>&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>search:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files relating to the site search engine.  No need to modify.</small><ul>
      <li>&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>sell:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files relating to selling issues.  No need to modify.</small><ul>
      <li>&nbsp;</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>sellers:</strong><ul>
      <li><font color="#ff0080">index.cfm</font>: <small>This file can be changed to add more information or graphics.</small></li>
    </ul> 
    <p><strong>thumbs:</strong>&nbsp;<small>This  directory contains files relating to the auction studio. No need to modify.</small><ul>
      <li><small></li>
    </ul>
    </SMALL>
    </td>
