    <td valign="top" colspan="2"><font color="#008000" 
           ><strong>Remember ...</strong></font><ul>
      <li>All generated pages will have a time stamp like this: &quot;<b>last updated:</b> 
                mm/dd/yyy, hh:mm:ss&quot;.&nbsp; These pages are scheduled to re-generate every 2 hours. &nbsp; In order to
        manually re-generate pages login to the administrator and click on the refresh button..</li>
    </ul>

	<font color="#008000"><strong>Modifying Tips ...</strong></font><ul>
      <li>It is best to modify the ".cfm" pages in Cold Fusion Studio or an Ascii Text Editor.
	  Some HTML editors don't recognize or may corrupt the Cold Fusion programming contained
	  within the file. If you are not sure whether your software will corrupt the programming,
	  it is best to start by making a back-up of the file before you begin modifications.</li></ul></p>
	
